      interface.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ITextureBuffer2DArray::unique_ptr CreateTextureBuffer2DArray();]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="ITextureBuffer2DArray!cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer2DArray">
        A freshly constructed <TypeRef>ITextureBuffer2DArray</TypeRef> object, wrapped in a <TypeRef>unique_ptr</TypeRef>.
      </ReturnValue>
